<div id="review_2098449262" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2098449262" />
    <a title="Claudia B" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/70517422-claudia-b"><img alt="Claudia B" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2098449262?book_show_action=true">Aug 20, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Claudia B" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Claudia B" href="/user/show/70517422-claudia-b">Claudia B</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781532006272" href="/book/show/33033660-betrayal-of-faith">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2098449262" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5442189036689956890">As an avid reader of John Grisham, Scott Turow, and David Baldacci, I rarely read novels from lesser or unknown authors. Seeing “Betrayal of Faith” on my Kindle picks list, I decided to give it a shot. I was pleasantly surprised. Mark Bello takes readers inside a “power group” (The Church) and shows how far its leaders will go to protect their darkest secrets. The scariest part is that while fiction, “Betrayal of Faith” doesn’t stretch far from reality.<br/><br/>I highly recommend this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

