<div id="review_3312705679" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3312705679" />
    <a title="John" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/58290169-john"><img alt="John" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3312705679?book_show_action=true">May 01, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="John" class="user" itemprop="url" name="John" href="/user/show/58290169-john">John</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/39944875-betrayal-of-justice">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=action-adventure">action-adventure</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=detective-story">detective-story</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=police-procedural">police-procedural</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/58290169-john?shelf=romantic-suspense">romantic-suspense</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3312705679" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18431154354946566533">This second book in the Zachary Blake Legal Thriller Series by Mark M Bello was loaded with intense and explosive action and suspense. One thing about the author, he is definitely not afraid to tackle sensitive and current subjects in his writings. This time it is about bigotry and hatred toward Muslims and all other non-white Christians. The main character, Ayra, is subjected to multiple physical and emotional attacks by both the police and the white-supremacists. Then, simmering on the back bu</span>
  <span id="freeText18431154354946566533" style="display:none">This second book in the Zachary Blake Legal Thriller Series by Mark M Bello was loaded with intense and explosive action and suspense. One thing about the author, he is definitely not afraid to tackle sensitive and current subjects in his writings. This time it is about bigotry and hatred toward Muslims and all other non-white Christians. The main character, Ayra, is subjected to multiple physical and emotional attacks by both the police and the white-supremacists. Then, simmering on the back burner of the story is the subject of deporting all Muslims from the USA per the president of the United States' executive order, as well as halting the incoming ones from certain countries. I can't wait to see what subject he attacks in book 3 of the series which I have already added to my TBR file. This is a voluntary review of a copy of this book from Fast and Free Reviews.</span>
